PrecisRe-appointment, effective March 10, 1994, during pleasure, for a term of two years, of Jean-Paul Duguay, of Gaspé, Quebec, as a Canadian representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization.

precis:
Re-appointment, effective March 10, 1994, during pleasure, for a term of
two years, of Jean-Paul Duguay, of Gaspé, Quebec, as a Canadian
representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation
Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic
Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of
